race.description: Boyle Estate Agents Muswellbrook Mdn Plate
race.comment: JUST JOAN (6) led and gave a great sight but found the winner a little too good when resuming from a 15-month spell over 900m at Coonabarabran last start. Should take great benefit from that outing. Tongue tie on is an interesting gear change. Looks the one to beat. TESORINO (9) wasn't beaten far when fresh from a spell over 900m here recently. Nicely drawn and can improve over the extra 100m. WANAVAN (3) is back from a brief spell. Placed four from ten including one here at this journey. Recent trial winner who looks ready for a strong return. THIEF OF JOY (10) is one for the wider exotics first-up from a seven-month spell. Gets a couple of key gear changes which may be significant. FINED FOR SPEEDING (1) debuts and is worth some thought after a good second in a recent Scone trial.
